 "name": "RPlog_Kubaz_Trandoshan_and_Wookiee",
 "title": "A Kubaz, a Trandoshan, and a Wookiee",
 "summary": "In the aftermath of the refinery explosion and attacks that rocked Cloud City, three friends on a break from the Caspian relief effort -- the Kubazian tailor Zubindi Hakoon, Trandoshan captain Drorq, and Wookiee politician Zaalbacca -- head into the Caspar Caf for coffee. There they cross paths with the harried acting Baroness-Administrator Quinne Stardust Rose and, to everyone's astonishment, find Johanna's ex Zeak Oppenhiemer moonlighting behind the bar, browbeating a long-suffering Rodian barista he insists on calling 'Jack.' Amid Zeak's absurd, increasingly chemical coffee experiments -- including a swamp-water brew Drorq happily downs -- the group trades gossip about Johanna's recovery and the investigation, orders elaborate drinks, and settles in as Zeak slips off toward the restrooms with a cryptic promise that the best is yet to come.",
